«c2»«ac»UPDATE ON WHAT'S HAPPENING IN THE WORLD OF AMIGA«»
«»
«c1»By Zerox/Gods«»
«»
«»
«as»
«c7»Almost one and a half year ago, in late October 2000, «c6»Amiga «c7»announced the first new
amiga hardware in 6 years. Just to recapture a bit. The first
product from the "new" amiga is called «c6»AmigaONE, «c7»and it will run a single
piece of software named «c6»Amiga Digital Environment (DE). «c7»The Amiga DE has
the ability to host itself on multiple hardware and operating system
platforms, which gives us all a chance to chose the hardware that best
suits our needs and taste. We can use a PC if we'd like, but the best
part is of course that our current amigas also can be upgraded to run
Amiga DE if I have understood this correctly.«»
«»
A partner of Amiga, «c6»Eyetech, «c7»got the mission to create some products to
achieve certain goals. With these add-in products, old amiga
machines will have a modern graphics chip, full classic compatibility,
G3/G4 CPUs and industry standard expansion options. And the machines will
be able to run the Amiga DE.«»
«»
«»
Anyway, the specification is following on the next page:«»
«»
«»
«»
«al»- CPU/One AmigaDE friendly host processor (x86, PPC, Arm, SH4, MIPS)«»
- Graphics: Next Generation Matrox graphic chips (probably G800)«»
- Sound: Creative EMU10K1 chip based audio card«»
- RAM: Minimum 64MB«»
- Drives: 10GB+ HD, DVD/CD player (both)«»
- Expansion: 2 free PCI slots, Firewire«»
- Other: 10/100 Mbps Ethernet, 56k modem, USB 1.0«»
«»
«»
«as»The first products based on the spesification mention, are The Amiga One
1200 PPC and the Amiga One 4000 PPC. These are add-in cards for the «c6»classic
A1200 and A4000. «c7»They will make use of PPC accelerator cards. These models
will dual both «c6»AmigaOS 3.9, «c7»and the new AmigaDE. These cards can infact
also be run without any A1200 or A4000 motherboard, but then without the
AmigaOS 3.9 compatilibility. bplan Gmbh will make stand alone Amiga One
computers with PowerPC processors. By the way, in AmigaOne, One stands for
it being a single processor. As you understand, Amiga will provide
the new revolutionary software and their partners the hardware.«»
«»
This was the news which we got a long time ago, but what has happened since
then?«»
«»
There were alot of announcements at the «c6»official amiga website, «c7»so let us
just take a brief look at all of these from the new beginning of Amiga Inc
until today.«»
